text: Hello! Just an update.  I have working on v1 the same end-to-end scenario in the Node SDK running in Java.  Does a deployment proposal to Peer, then Orderer (commit) for that deployment. Does then the same for Invoke for that deployment and finally does a Query.  There are some changes on Master which I still need to catch up to and ALOT of cleanup.  I'm hoping to have this ready by the end of week.
